remarks.p:
By default, a 'chevron' is displayed in the foreground for this element.
If an image is specified in its appearance, that image is displayed instead;
this property determines the size at which that image is displayed.

member.summary:
Returns the resolved value of the  property.
If the property has been set to a non-default value, that value is returned;
otherwise, the return value is based on the control's  property.
